Package DAO

Class CustDAO

  • java.lang.Object
    • DAO.CustDAO
  • public class CustDAO
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to interact with the connected database and all Customer objects made. This class includes the Create, Read, Update, and Delete actions associated with the database.
